Dutch
Red Bovie (Robert Duvall), een Texaanse ranch-eigenaar, wordt gedwongen

English

Red Bovie isn't about to go quietly to the dismal trailer park that's all
he can now afford, and instead goes off with his grandson Gally - son of
his long-estranged son Jimmy - for one last wild and woolly adventure
during a night in Old Mexico.
